column5: Felt so good to finally hook up with a buddy for a well deserved day of fishing. No hospitals, clinics, waiting rooms or errands for one and all. Just 2 Grumps, a lot of ice and some misguided fish. Bill's catch.  My catch   Now the puppy and I can have our weekly fish brekkie.  Shore ice should be in pretty poor shape, down here in Niagara, by the weekend
nice,   and a well deserved break from the sounds of it
That one in the middle looks like a slab, nice
Nice harvest! So Bill caught his on the ice and you caught yours in the sink?
Nice going Bruce & Co.      Lots of beauties in that haul    Enjoy your breaky
mmmmmm....perch breaky...yummy some nice ones there for sure...
Nice!!  Spring Perching, Gotta Luv it.  Rick
Nice catch, sounds like it was long overdue and well deserved, enjoy
Great to see you made it out, and a successful outing at that.
